PRESIDENT TRUMP has delayed some tariffs on Chinese imports. Soumaya Keynes, our US economics editor, explains the surprise decision and its implications for the global economy. Also, is data as valuable an asset as oil? What can companies learn from the oil industry about keeping data safe? And, the secrets of success for online fashion retailers. Rachana Shanbogue hosts. Runtime: 21 min    Listen on: Apple Podcasts | Spotify | Google | Stitcher | TuneIn